sections.heading: dispensing permit; liability; when
sections.text: The delegating pharmacist or the on-call pharmacist shall not be held liable for acts or omissions on the part of an individual dispensing pursuant to the delegated dispensing permit.SourceLaws 1994, LB 900, ยง 22;Laws 2001, LB 398, ยง 58;R.S.1943, (2003), ยง 71-1,147
